userdoc.notice: Deposita tokens (ETH/ERC20) y los convierte automáticamente a USDC vía Uniswap V2 Router,         acreditando al usuario el USDC resultante. Garantiza que el total en USDC nunca supere bankCapUsd.

params._bankCapUsd: bank cap expressed in USDC smallest units (e.g. 100 * 10**6)

params.minUsdcOut: minimum acceptable USDC out to protect from slippage (USDC smallest units)

params.amountIn: amount of token being deposited (in token units)
params.minUsdcOut: minimum acceptable USDC out to protect from slippage (USDC smallest units)

params.amountUsdc: amount of USDC in USDC smallest units (6 decimals)
